  "description": "<p>屏幕作为iPhone、iPad等智能设备最重要的构造部件之一，在保证性能的前提下，当然是越薄越好。玻璃厂商方面，康宁的大猩猩Gorilla玻璃是苹果iPhone 5的选择，但在玻璃配置在屏幕面板中本身的强度如何，却还要更细致的考虑到诸多方面的因素。<strong>最近苹果在欧洲专利局获得了一项专利，该专利是可以加固设备超薄玻璃的一套系统，名为“Glass Ion Exchange Bath”（玻璃离子交换室），通过这种方式处理的超薄玻璃，可以改善强度，更适用于覆盖LCD屏幕以及类似iPhone的屏幕。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e04ce28/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243007.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%9B%BAiOS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%85%E8%96%84%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243007.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%9B%BAiOS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%85%E8%96%84%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243007.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%9B%BAiOS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%85%E8%96%84%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243007.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%9B%BAiOS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%85%E8%96%84%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B